item.title: Python Blog
item.description: Introduction: In this blog, I will be writing about what I have learned in a Computational Biology course I took. Now if you were expecting a blog about snakes, I am sorry to disappoint; however, I promise this blog about the language Python is just as riveting! In this course, we were briefly introduced to Python. I will be including a few things that I found were interesting in this blog post such as using the package “Reticulate”, regular expression, and some things about python bioinformatics.
